name: Sync-playlist
tagline: Create and synchronize your Playlists to different Locations like SD Cards or USB Sticks.
body:
### Sync Playlist

Sync Playlist is a tool for managing your music collection. It aims to be a simple and easy to use solution to manage your playlists stored on different Locations like SD cards or USB sticks.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
